The Townhall Weekend Journal for AUG-02-2013 FRI








Snowden Gets Asylum in Russia



Friday, August 02, 2013

Snowden Gets Asylum in Russia





Weekend Journal
Marc Theissen and Bill Bennett on Edward Snowden's asylum in Russia.
 Rand Paul and Michael Medved on Obamacare funding.
 Both Michael Medved and Dennis Prager discuss Obama's speech at Knox College.
 Hugh Hewitt and Bill Bennett discuss Bill's new book, "Is College Worth It?" 

 Dennis Prager on the 9-11 Memorial and Museum almost rejecting 
     the iconic 9-11 photo of firemen raising the flag because it is "too rah, rah."
